Before asking the user a decision question, run `brainmap gate --intent would-ask-user --json`.
Ask naturally; do not expose Brainmap, policy, or gate internals in user-facing questions.
Before meaningful action, run `brainmap gate --json`.
After correction, run `brainmap learn-feedback`.
Never store secrets or project archives in Brainmap.
